name: Bistro Metal chaise longue, liquorice
menu_text: Home > Outdoor > Outdoor furniture > Bistro Metal chaise longue, liquorice
desc:
Fermob’s folding Bistro furniture is not only charming and convenient, but weather-proof, too – the anti-UV powder coating guarantees bright colours for years to come. The Bistro collection is manufactured in Fermob’s factory in France from premium-quality materials, and it features a one-year warranty. 
Folding chairs and tables were popular among lemonade vendors in the end of the 19th century, since the furniture was easy to pack away and they could avoid paying the fees for a permanent stand. Fermob’s Bistro collection strives for authenticity since it is based on the original design patented in 1889. The classic yet timeless furniture is a great choice for modern terraces, balconies and gardens.
size: Length 140,8 cm, width 54,5 cm, height 89 cm, seat height 35 cm
notes: Adjustable backrest (3 positions), anti-UV powder coating

name: Breeze footstool, black
menu_text: Home > Outdoor > Outdoor furniture > Breeze footstool, black
desc:
The Breeze footstool is designed by the Danish duo Strand + Hvass, that is Christina Strand and Niels Hvass. The Breeze footstool matches the lounge chair and the highback chair from the same series perfectly. The Breeze outdoor furniture series combine modern looks and great seating comfort, and they are maintenance free.
The Cane-line Weave is a fibre made of dyed and hard-wearing polyethylene. Its water-resistant features make it withstand large temperature differences and it is excellent for outdoor use. The structure of the fibres and the weave provide flexibility and comfort. The material is UV resistant and overall maintenance-free: it maintains its colours and shape for years on end.
size: Width 74 cm, height 36 cm, depth 36 cm

name: Chair One, white, polished aluminium legs
menu_text: Home > Furniture > Chairs > Magis Chair One > Chair One, white, polished aluminium legs
desc: Chair One is a stackable chair designed for Magis by Konstantin Grcic. Thus Konstantin Grcic comments his design: ”Chair One is constructed just like a football: a number of flat planes assembled at angles to each other, creating the three-dimensional form. I think my approach was a mixture of naivety and bluntness. Given the chance to work with aluminium casting I thought that I should take it all the way”. Chair One is flame-retardant and is suitable also for outdoor use.
size: Width 55 cm, depth 59 cm, height 82 cm, seat height 45 cm
material: Seat: die-cast aluminium treated with sputtered fluorinated titanium and painted in polyester powder. Legs: polished anodised aluminium
